# API Spec

# Group Users
## User list [/users]
### Create user [POST]

+ Request
  + Headers
    Content-Type: application/json
  + Body
    { "username": "Linus", "password": "test" }

+ Response 201
  + Headers
    Content-Type: application/json
    Location: /users/{userId}
  + Body
    { "id": "{userId}", "username": "Linus", "password": "test" }

### List users [GET]

+ Response 200
  + Headers
    Content-Type: application/json
  + Body
    [
      { "id": "{userId}", "username": "Linus" }
    ]

## User [/users/{userId}]
### Get user [GET]

+ Response 200
  + Headers
    Content-Type: application/json
  + Body
    { "id": "{userId}", "username": "Linus" }

# Group Session
