# Group Messages
## Message List [/messages]
### Post message [POST]

+ Request
  + Headers
    Content-Type: application/json
  + Body
    { "text": "Listen to me!" }

+ Response 201
  + Headers
    Content-Type: application/json
    Location: /messages/{messageId}
  + Body
    { "id": "{messageId}", "text": "Listen to me!" }

### List messages [GET]

+ Response 200
  + Headers
    Content-Type: application/json
  + Body
    [
      { "id": "{messageId}", "text": "Listen to me!" }
    ]

## Message [/messages/{messageId}]
### Get message [GET]

+ Response 200
  + Headers
    Content-Type: application/json
  + Body
    { "id": "{messageId}", "text": "Listen to me!" }

### Delete message [DELETE]

+ Response 204
